name: Jaiho Crypto
additional_notices: Kindly be aware of liquidity-related risks. This notice is not directed at any project in particular, and is more of a cautionary reminder.

description.en: JaiHo is India’s first community-based crypto project with low supply, which is deflationary over time. JaiHo’s unique revenue-sharing model includes a charity mission. We have built a community before releasing a token—No Big Promises, just a loyal Community to grow over time.
